title: Did the woman die after smashing her head in the car door in the garage?
subtitle: It was reported that the 23-year-old child was trying to obtain a credit card that had been dropped.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: A 23-year-old woman died in Ohio after she hung her head between the door of her car and his tyre after collided with a drive-by machine in a parking garage.
